How to Build
============

1) First create the libpcff libraries and install them
2) run make
3) test
   socketTest -help prints out startup info
   
   in one window start up a UDP server (use defaults)
   socketTest

   in another window start up the UDP echo client
   socketTest -testType client -testStr helloWorld

Unix Socket Tests
---------------------

./sockTest -testType UnixDGRAMserver
./sockTest -testType UnixDGRAMclient

The file descriptors are written by default in the /tmp dir
sockClientTest, and sockServerTest
